 2000-03572000-03-230,  ,  INDUSTRY,  , 
PrecisSanctionning of BY-LAW NO. 47 as adopted by THE CANADIAN MEDICAL PROTECTIVE ASSOCIATION at its annual meeting in Ottawa on August 25, 1999, which, inter alia, adds the new territory of Nunavut to the description of Geographic Area 2, thereby making it possible for its members in Nunavut to be eligible for election to the Council.
Attachments
precis:
Sanctionning of BY-LAW NO. 47 as adopted by THE CANADIAN MEDICAL PROTECTIVE
ASSOCIATION at its annual meeting in Ottawa on August 25, 1999, which,
inter alia, adds the new territory of Nunavut to the description of
Geographic Area 2, thereby making it possible for its members in Nunavut
to be eligible for election to the Council.
